data.oai_dc:dc: This is an Oksrukuyuk Creek bottomsample. The file simply lists the length of each insect measured, as wellas when and where along the creek it was captured. Only the actualmeasurements of the insects are listed, for example, if there wasn't aparticular insect found from a replicate at a station, then that stationisn't listed either. This file is captured baetis.
